{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2029, "height": 2747, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "陕西瓦云驿丞少泉杜公三光墓\n\n生于□□拾年\n\n卒于崇祯陆年\n\n子杜从龙杜化龙杜相龙杜腾龙\n孙男杜琨杜璋杜瑛杜廪\n杜□杜□杜□\n玄孙杜师故\n\n", "block_bbox": [272, 249, 1039, 705], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "重刻槐树岭碑文序", "block_bbox": [279, 860, 622, 903], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "槐树岭村旧有地基石碑一座。近来风雨剥蚀、不时倒塌。万寿监生向荣等，恐其至后无凭，故将旧碑竖起，更立碑楼以取固。犹恐世远年湮，不免剥蚀倒塌之患，又将原碑文另刻一石，存诸祠堂，永志不朽。碑文列后：", "block_bbox": [189, 929, 1090, 1238], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "前明洪武时，余始祖自山西洪桐迁至坻坞。嘉靖万历间，自四世祖敕赐义民讳真金、五世祖瓦云驿丞讳三光、北讳三乐时，家货颇丰，乃承国制，口官马以共差役此地则坻坞。适县之□也。树槐于此，为往来游畋之所。口口石桥之南（以下文字缺）\n", "block_bbox": [192, 1261, 1090, 1640], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "程\n\n", "block_bbox": [1169, 248, 1669, 1635], "block_id": 4, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "例授文林郎借补考城县儒学训导韶峰杜老先生两世遗慕碑\n", "block_bbox": [193, 1732, 1330, 1842], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "韶峰杜老先生，讳含章，字子贞，乾隆乙卯科房元，其为人孝友醇实，笃嗜读书，其为文宏深雅健，雄视一世，又邃于《天文志》《地理图》《律吕精义》《皇极经世》诸书，所著有《易经句解》《书经句解》《四书述要》，待梓。生平好接引后学，游其门者绳陕新邑，多知名士。暮岁司铎考城，奖进士子，惟恐不及，其素性然也。子三：次文琅，中年早逝；长讳文琳，字口美，号崑甫先生，弱冠游庠，克承家学，且天性醇，谨，循循善诱，近而亲族，远而太康、长垣等邑，启迪之广，几与老先生声望相等；三文茂，生性镇静，绰有父风，皆老先生之遗泽也。吁以老先生之醇正渊博，不克扬", "block_bbox": [190, 1866, 1332, 2517], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "例授文林郎树考城縣儒学训学站举社老先生雨世道", "block_bbox": [1367, 1736, 1663, 2505], "block_id": 7, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "", "block_bbox": [1763, 489, 1865, 570], "block_id": 8, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1781, 735, 1859, 1437], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三七〇", "block_bbox": [1790, 2080, 1841, 2194], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 8}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9759114384651184, "coordinate": [190.476318359375, 1866.8509521484375, 1332.342041015625, 2517.50927734375]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9677491188049316, "coordinate": [1169.517578125, 248.08721923828125, 1669.60888671875, 1635.7958984375]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9614085555076599, "coordinate": [1367.063720703125, 1736.293701171875, 1663.32470703125, 2505.916748046875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9562598466873169, "coordinate": [192.60800170898438, 1261.870849609375, 1090.8812255859375, 1640.248291015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9379623532295227, "coordinate": [189.0806884765625, 929.1007080078125, 1090.7274169921875, 1238.1607666015625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7776760458946228, "coordinate": [193.9453125, 1732.794189453125, 1330.143310546875, 1842.497802734375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7182048559188843, "coordinate": [279.369873046875, 860.7955322265625, 622.0596923828125, 903.2135009765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.691743791103363, "coordinate": [272.5438232421875, 249.33587646484375, 1039.0958251953125, 705.552734375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5637181997299194, "coordinate": [1790.8431396484375, 2080.606201171875, 1841.4552001953125, 2194.932373046875]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.521016001701355, "coordinate": [1763.543212890625, 489.38525390625, 1865.600830078125, 570.5870361328125]}